            "title": "eGain announces increase to stock repurchase program of $20 million",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>eGain (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EGAN\" title=\"eGain Corporation\">EGAN</a></span>) announced on Thursday that its Board of Directors approved a $20 million increase in its stock repurchase program, bringing the aggregate amount eGain may purchase from $40 million to $60 million of its outstanding common stock.</li>\n<li>The stock repurchase program will be funded using existing cash or future cash flows.</li>\n<li>EGAN <span style=\"color: green;\">+0.81%</span> after hours to $6.22.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20222331-egain-announces-increase-to-stock-repurchase-program-of-20-million\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
