            "id": "4492456",
            "title": "Cross Country Health gains amid certifying compliance with FTC for Aya deal",
            "description": "<html><body><p>Cross Country Healthcare (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CCRN\" title=\"Cross Country Healthcare, Inc.\">CCRN</a></span>)<span style=\"color: #008000;\"> rose 6.2%</span> at least partly after the company and Aya agreed to certify compliance with the Federal Trade Commission for their deal. </p>\n<p>Cross Country (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CCRN\" title=\"Cross Country Healthcare, Inc.\">CCRN</a></span>) and Aya disclosed the companies had certified that they had substantially complied with the FTC's second request as of Aug. 29, according to an<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/filing/10382337\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" 8-K \"> 8-K </a>filing on Wednesday. The deal is expected to close in Q4. The termination date for the deal was also automatically extended until Dec. 3 from Sept. 3.</p>\n<p>In March, Cross Country (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CCRN#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\" title=\"Cross Country Healthcare, Inc.\">CCRN</a>) received a<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4412167-cross-country-healthcare-aya-get-2nd-request-from-ftc-on-deal#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" second request f\"> second request f</a>rom the FTC about the travel nursing company's planned sale to Aya.</p>\n<p>Aya Healthcare in December entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Cross Country <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362496-cross-country-healthcare-stock-soars-on-acquisition-by-aya-healthcare-for-1861share#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"for $18.61/share in cash\">for $18.61/share in cash.</a></p>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1352553853/image_1352553853.jpg?io=getty-c-w750",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4492456-cross-country-health-gains-amid-certifying-compliance-with-ftc-for-avaya-deal",
